data.description: Welcome to paradise! This beautiful home in West Feliciana Parish is located in the tranquil community of Lake Rosemound.  It features a majestic tree lined corner lot, covered wrap-around porch that allows you the opportunity to enjoy the lazy days of summer and cool nights of winter. The large yard is an entertainer's dream, offering plenty of space for parking and outdoor activities. There is also an outdoor shower, fire pit, fenced in backyard, and a storage shed to keep all of your lawn and lake essentials neatly tucked away. Once inside you will notice an open and airy floor plan that offers tons of natural lighting, vaulted ceilings, center island, French doors leading to the covered porch, and laminate flooring throughout. This home is a rare find in a great community. Schedule your private showing to come discover all it has to offer.  Buyer to pay $2500 lake membership transfer fee at closing.
